☎️ Recruiter Call 常見問題（口語版答案）

⸻

1️⃣ 自我介紹
Q: Tell me about yourself
👉 
	•	Hi, I’m Mike.
	•	I’m currently working at Taishin Bank, focusing on AML systems.
	•	My work mainly involves system integration, SQL data validation, and ETL processes.
	•	I also worked in Singapore before, supporting automation using C# and SQL.
	•	So overall, I have around 5 years of experience in backend systems.

⸻

5️⃣ 為什麼想去新加坡
Q: Why Singapore?
👉 
	•	I’ve worked in Singapore before, so I’m familiar with the environment.
	•	I’d like to gain more exposure to international banking systems.

⸻

6️⃣ 為什麼想換工作
Q: Why are you looking for a new opportunity?
👉 
	•	I’ve learned a lot in my current role.
	•	But I’m looking for more exposure to larger-scale systems and international projects.
	•	That’s why I’m exploring opportunities in Singapore.

⸻


7️⃣ 目前狀態

Q: Are you interviewing with other companies?

👉 口語版：
	•	I’ve started exploring a few opportunities.
	•	But I’m mainly focusing on roles that match my background.

