2️⃣ AML 經驗
Q: Can you tell me about your AML experience?
👉 
	•	Sure. I mainly work on the technical side of AML systems.
	•	I handle backend integration and data validation using SQL.
	•	I also support ETL processes and data migration.
	•	It’s mostly about making sure the data is accurate and compliant.

⸻

3️⃣ Control-M

Q: Do you have experience with Control-M?

👉 口語版：
	•	Yes, I’ve worked with Control-M.
	•	I mainly handle monitoring and supporting batch jobs in production.
	•	Making sure everything runs smoothly.

