4️⃣ SQL / 技術能力

Q: How’s your SQL?

👉 口語版：
	•	I’d say I’m comfortable with SQL.
	•	I mainly use it for data validation and troubleshooting.
	•	Also for supporting system implementation.

⸻


8️⃣ 合約工作

Q: Are you okay with contract roles?

👉 口語版：
	•	Yes, I’m open to contract roles.
	•	As long as the scope is relevant and there’s a good learning opportunity.

⸻




9️⃣ 到職時間

Q: When can you start?

👉 口語版：
	•	I’d need about one month notice.
	•	But I can be flexible if needed.

⸻

🔟 薪水（重點🔥）

Q: What’s your expected salary?

👉 第一招（最推薦）：
	•	I’m open to discussion based on the role.
	•	May I know the budget range for this position?

👉 如果被逼一定要講：
	•	I’m looking at around X to X SGD, depending on the scope.

（👉 不確定數字可以先問我）

⸻

1️⃣1️⃣ 可面試時間

Q: When are you available for a call?

👉 口語版：
	•	I’m available after work hours,
	•	or during lunch break,
	•	or on weekends.

⸻

1️⃣2️⃣ 結尾反問（一定要問🔥）

Q: Do you have any questions?

👉 口語版（選一個就好）：
	•	Yeah, could you share more about the team?
	•	Or what they’re mainly looking for in this role?

⸻

💡 超實用小技巧（讓你聽起來更自然）

你可以多加這些口語開頭👇
	•	“Yeah, sure.”
	•	“I’d say…”
	•	“Mainly…”
	•	“So yeah…”

👉 例如：

Yeah, I’d say I’m quite comfortable with SQL.

⸻

🔥 最後重點（真的差很多）

👉 每題控制在「2～4句」
👉 不要背太死，要像聊天
👉 關鍵字要一直出現：
AML / SQL / ETL / Control-M / Banking

